              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "incident_source": [
                  "TAGD"
                ],
                "reaction": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                "  Tagged  photon facility of the MAX-lab at the",
                " University of Lund.",
                " 64 plastic  scintillators  in the focal plane of the",
                " tagging spectrometer gave  tagged  photons  with  an",
                " energy resolution of DeltaEg about 330 keV.",
                "Focal plane was divided in two halves which gave mean",
                " tagged photon energies of Eg ~ 43.7 and 52.0 MeV."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "A 50.1  (0.5) mg/cm**2 99.97%  pure Bi foil supported",
                " by a 66.1 (0.5)  mg/cm**2  polyethylene  teraphalate",
                " film  was  placed  at  the  29.0 (0.5) degree to the",
                " photon beam direction."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TELES",
                "SISD",
                "HPGE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Two  telescopes  each consisting of",
                " two silicon strip detectors (SSDS) and one hyperpure",
                " germanium detector (HPGE).  In total, the telescopes",
                " covered  the  angular range THETA-p = 50 -130 degree",
                " and subtended a solid angle of ~ 500 msr."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
